title: Lowest Methane Emissions from Industrial Processes
description: In 2023, the Philippines recorded one of the lowest methane emissions from industrial processes, with only 0.0001 Mt CO2e.

title: High Medium and High-Tech Exports
description: In 2022, 80.02% of the Philippines' manufactured exports were medium and high-tech, indicating a strong technological export sector.

title: Low Wanted Fertility Rate
description: The wanted fertility rate in the Philippines was 1.5 births per woman in 2022, one of the lowest globally.

title: High Women's Share of Population Living with HIV
description: In 2022, 6.63% of women aged 15 and older in the Philippines were living with HIV, a concerning statistic.
